# ğŸ§  MNIST GAN Generator with Streamlit

This project implements a Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) using Keras to generate handwritten digits from the MNIST dataset. It includes an interactive Streamlit web interface to train the model and generate synthetic digits.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Train a GAN on the MNIST dataset.
- Generate handwritten digits using a trained generator.
- Interactive web interface built with Streamlit.
- Save and load generator weights.
- Visualize generated images in a grid layout.

